<h3>Virtual Rock Laboratory</h3>
<p>
The Virtual Rock Laboratory is a web portal that allows running <a href="https://launchpad.net/esys-particle">ESyS-Particle</a>
Discrete Element (DEM) simulations on the ARCS/AuScope computational Grid.
For more information about the Virtual Rock Laboratory please go to the
</p>
<a href="https://twiki.auscope.org/twiki/bin/view/Grid/ProjectVRLUserGuide">Virtual Rock Lab User's Guide</a>.
<p>
To access the Virtual Rock Laboratory now, please follow this link:
</p>
<p><a href="https://portal.esscc.uq.edu.au/vrl">Virtual Rock Laboratory</a>
</p>
<h3>Escript Portal</h3>
The Escript Portal is a web portal that allows running <a href="https://launchpad.net/escript-finley">Escript/Finley</a>
Finite Element (FEM) simulations on the ARCS/AuScope computational Grid.
For more information about the Escript Portal please refer to the
<a href="https://twiki.esscc.uq.edu.au/bin/twiki/view/ESSCC/EscriptPortalUserGuide">Escript Portal User's Guide</a>.

<p>
To access the Escript Portal now, please follow this link:
</p>
<p><a href="https://portal.esscc.uq.edu.au/escript">Escript Portal</a>
</p>

